\subsection{Comparative Performance Analysis of Nodal vs. Mesh Analysis Algorithms \hfill May 2024 -- June 2024}
\begin{itemize}[leftmargin=*,noitemsep]
    \item Reduced circuit-solving runtime by up to 35\% by implementing and optimizing Nodal and Mesh analysis algorithms in both C and Python, leveraging efficient data structures and minimizing redundant computations.
    \item Benchmarked algorithmic performance across 100+ circuit configurations, demonstrating that Nodal Analysis outperformed Mesh Analysis in large sparse networks, while Mesh Analysis excelled in planar low-loop circuits.
    \item Improved memory efficiency by 28\% through custom matrix representations and optimized solver routines, enabling faster simulations on resource-constrained embedded systems.
    \item Validated cross-language execution metrics using Python's profiling tools and C-based memory tracing, contributing to a reproducible and platform-independent evaluation framework for algorithm selection in VLSI circuit simulators.
\end{itemize}

